3.name: Narration
3.text:
A rough and beastly large man, who looks like he's
feasting on the spoils of war, is gulping down
alcohol while sinking his teeth into what appears
to be the thigh meat of a beast. His underlings
are likely scavenging valuable items from the
remains of today's loot.

4.name: Thief A
4.text:
"Boss, today's haul seems to be quite a good one,
isn't it?"

5.name: Thief B
5.text:
"Hehe, with this, it looks like we won't have to
worry about alcohol for a while."

6.name: Thief Boss
6.text:
"......By the way, have those thieves who went
after that pickpocket come back yet?"

7.name: Thief C
7.text:
"They're taking their sweet time... They should
have caught that kind of woman and come back by
now."

8.name: Thief Boss
8.text:
"Tch, if they keep me waiting and go after her,
I'll punch them!"

11.name: Eni-sensei
11.text:
(There are four left. It seems like this is
everyone. What should we do? Sol)

12.name: Sol
12.text:
(...Here I go! I'll do my best to bring them
down!)

19.name: Narration
19.text:
The leader of the pickpockets was defeated, the
others who surrendered were captured, and those
who resisted until the end were abandoned.
Considering the deeds they committed against
innocent people, this was still a fairly lenient
treatment.
